    "7: Exemplary in breadth; delivers outstanding coverage, thoroughly detailing all crucial aspects of the topic without including irrelevant information.",
    "Verifiability 1: No supporting evidence; claims are unsubstantiated.",
    "2: Rarely supported with evidence; many claims are unsubstantiated.",
    "3: Inconsistently verified; some claims are supported; evidence is occasionally provided.",
    "4: Generally verified; claims are usually supported with evidence; however, there might be a few instances where verification is lacking 5: Well-supported; claims are very well supported with credible evidence, and instances of unsupported claims are rare."
